<section id="itsm_taSource">
    <title>its_taSource</title>
    
    <para>Text Analysis Source - the <code>its_taSource</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
        is the <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink> defined
            <code>its_taSource</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>.</para>
    <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
        string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> text.</para>
    <para>The text string is supposed to be a human or machine redable name of a collection of text
        analysis concept resources, in the sense of an <ulink
            url="http://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#textAnalysis-info-pieces"> identifier of the collection
            source</ulink>.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis>: undefined.</para>
    
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
            targetdoc="../../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk"><code>&lt;mrk></code></olink>,
        and <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sm.xml" targetptr="sm"
                ><code>&lt;sm></code></olink>.</para>
    
    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Constraints</title>
        <listitem><para>When the <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
                <link linkend="itsm_taSource"><code>its_taSource</code></link> is set, the <olink
                    targetdoc="itsm_taIdent.xml" targetptr="itsm_taIdent"
                    ><code>its_taIdent</code></olink>
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
                <glossterm>must</glossterm> be set as well.</para></listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <para>See the <olink targetdoc="../../modules/itsm/Text_Analysis.xml" targetptr="taAnnotation"
            >ITS Text Analysis Annotation</olink> for the full normative usage description of this
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>.
        Other advanced Constraints follow from that normative usage description.</para>
    
</section>
